This is the complete documentation of my final year project Megabolt.
It is free, cross platform, accelerated, schedulable, configurable
and friendly download manager.

Its completely written in Qt. And it features
* Threaded download
* Schedulable downloads
* Friendly and light-weight software
* Support Cache proxy
* Automated login downloads

Future Plans
* Extend protocol support to FTP, HTTPS, metalink . etc 
* Session - based or cookie enabled downloads
* Browser plugins to make the download stuff more easy

